To mitigate the vulnerability, you should change the condition in the `if` statement to check if at least 50% of the tokens have been delegated after three months have passed, instead of checking if the total delegated tokens exceed the total purchased tokens. This can be done by adding a modifier to the `delegation.holder` function:
